A cyberpunk-style illustration of a sleek hummingbird made of glowing circuit boards and neon-lit microchips, hovering mid-flight against a dark cityscape backdrop with rain-slicked streets reflecting purple and electric blue lights. The bird's wings are translucent holographic panels showing cascading streams of luminous data particles. Its body is constructed from interconnected geometric shapes resembling modular software components, with tiny glowing nodes at each connection point. Steam rises from nearby industrial pipes, and distant skyscrapers feature massive holographic advertisements. The scene conveys speed, efficiency, and the marriage of natural elegance with cutting-edge technology—a small but powerful creature built for performance in a complex digital ecosystem.
